name: 空 (Sora)
description:
空 (Sora)
Stay! No. This is not what I want.
Say! Why you are let me go?
See me,  so that I see you deeper oh deeper.
Are you not gonna miss me? Are you not gonna need me?
It hurts… It hurts…
Our memories keep haunting
You are the one that push me, then…

The world cruel sometimes
Everything’s taken
You’ve got nothing
Believe me, It’s fine
Keep moving on baby
The world cruel sometimes
Everything’s taken
You’ve got nothing
Fly with your wings
Sky answering at the end
I’m flying…
Flying with my wings
Cruising the night, and
Sing this song…
Sky answering at the end

DESCRIPTION
This song conveys a message of support to those who also feel that dealing with post-traumatic and tragic loss can then get to the stage of gathering reasons and tips to keep moving forward.

Tone Library (Jovan Yudistira and Pascalis Yoga)

Collaborated with:
DJ (Jandiek Firmanda)
Vocal (Della Dewinni)
Visual Animator (Fernanda Brelin)
